For creating a resource we shall use POST

when creation a resource then obviously the client shall send the entire request
by using the following URL's

/vacations or /vacations/{id}/reviews

Whenever the request is successful then the server shall a status code of 201

Along with 201 
Option 1:
it has the two options of providing the information back to the client 
it can send back the complete URL of the resource created 
example 
/vacations/121/reviews/2

option 2:
or May return the entire new object

In case of failure
it will send the http response code such 4XX(Client Error) or 5XX(Server Error)
along with the error message

